text: "What About Me?" is a 1984 song by Kenny Rogers, Kim Carnes and James Ingram. It is the leading single from his 16th studio album What About Me?. It went to number 15 in the United States, number 18 in Canada and number 49 in Australia. ==References== Category:1984 songs Category:1980s ballads Category:Kenny Rogers songs Category:James Ingram songs Category:Kim Carnes songs
title: What About Me? (Kenny Rogers song)
